00:30:42,640 --> 00:30:44,200
[SPEAKER_02] Kada ljudi shvate

738
00:30:44,200 --> 00:30:45,779
[SPEAKER_02] da vi njima manipulirate,

739
00:30:45,779 --> 00:30:47,220
[SPEAKER_02] oni se neće,

740
00:30:47,220 --> 00:30:48,380
[SPEAKER_02] dovešće u pitanje

741
00:30:48,380 --> 00:30:49,380
[SPEAKER_02] ono što je razumno.

742
00:30:49,380 --> 00:30:51,819
[SPEAKER_02] I onda imamo pravi kaos.

743
00:30:51,819 --> 00:30:52,180
[SPEAKER_02] Da.

744
00:30:52,180 --> 00:30:53,640
[SPEAKER_02] A bojim se da je to ono

745
00:30:53,640 --> 00:30:54,579
[SPEAKER_02] što se nama događa.

746
00:30:54,579 --> 00:30:54,940
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle,

747
00:30:54,940 --> 00:30:56,880
[SPEAKER_02] a sad više i sve jedno,

748
00:30:56,880 --> 00:30:58,220
[SPEAKER_02] je li super ili nije cijepice,

749
00:30:58,220 --> 00:31:00,359
[SPEAKER_02] budući da je ta mogućnost nestala.

750
00:31:00,359 --> 00:31:02,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ja jedno čekam čut objašnjenje

751
00:31:02,440 --> 00:31:04,180
[SPEAKER_00] zašto je to super da se to dogodilo.

752
00:31:04,740 --> 00:31:05,720
[SPEAKER_00] Kako je to genijalno.

753
00:31:05,720 --> 00:31:07,079
[SPEAKER_00] U stvari je isplanirano da mi...

754
00:31:07,079 --> 00:31:08,240
[SPEAKER_02] Pa veriti ćemo slušati o tome

755
00:31:08,240 --> 00:31:09,420
[SPEAKER_02] je li netko nešto čitao,

756
00:31:09,420 --> 00:31:10,880
[SPEAKER_02] kako netko ima frizuru,

757
00:31:10,880 --> 00:31:12,539
[SPEAKER_02] je li ovako nešto drugo sporednično.

758
00:31:12,539 --> 00:31:14,279
[SPEAKER_02] Ne se pruč za obzirajte za rješenje.

759
00:31:14,279 --> 00:31:15,259
[SPEAKER_00] A odgovora nema.

760
00:31:15,259 --> 00:31:16,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ti se nalaziš sad

761
00:31:16,599 --> 00:31:18,099
[SPEAKER_00] u jednoj specifičnej situaciji

762
00:31:18,099 --> 00:31:19,559
[SPEAKER_00] da si ti saborska zastupnica

763
00:31:19,559 --> 00:31:20,960
[SPEAKER_00] zajedno sa svojim mužem.

764
00:31:20,960 --> 00:31:21,559
[SPEAKER_00] I dakle,

765
00:31:21,559 --> 00:31:23,859
[SPEAKER_00] zanima me taj sad ugov.

766
00:31:23,859 --> 00:31:25,119
[SPEAKER_00] Vi imate malo djete.

767
00:31:25,119 --> 00:31:25,900
[SPEAKER_00] Kako to,

768
00:31:25,900 --> 00:31:28,200
[SPEAKER_00] kako se uspijevaš organizirati?

769
00:31:28,200 --> 00:31:28,440
[SPEAKER_00] Evo,

770
00:31:28,759 --> 00:31:30,079
[SPEAKER_00] imaš posao na faksu.

771
00:31:30,079 --> 00:31:32,140
[SPEAKER_00] Da li je tebi teže,

772
00:31:32,140 --> 00:31:33,079
[SPEAKER_00] da li je nini teže,

773
00:31:33,079 --> 00:31:34,359
[SPEAKER_00] da li je vama jednako teško?

774
00:31:34,359 --> 00:31:35,440
[SPEAKER_01] Uvijek je meni najteže.

775
00:31:35,440 --> 00:31:36,900
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je najteže.

776
00:31:36,900 --> 00:31:37,579
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, dobro.

777
00:31:37,579 --> 00:31:40,180
[SPEAKER_01] I neka se vi to zaprinali i važe.

778
00:31:40,180 --> 00:31:40,420
[SPEAKER_01] Iako,

779
00:31:40,420 --> 00:31:41,460
[SPEAKER_01] meni je najteže,

780
00:31:41,460 --> 00:31:44,140
[SPEAKER_01] a njemu je još teže,

781
00:31:44,140 --> 00:31:45,640
[SPEAKER_01] jer kad je meni najteže,

782
00:31:45,640 --> 00:31:47,319
[SPEAKER_01] onda ja napadam njega.

783
00:31:47,319 --> 00:31:47,500
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

784
00:31:47,500 --> 00:31:48,140
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle,

785
00:31:48,140 --> 00:31:49,519
[SPEAKER_01] on je krajnja žrtva.

786
00:31:49,519 --> 00:31:50,500
[SPEAKER_01] On je krajnja žrtva

787
00:31:50,500 --> 00:31:51,440
[SPEAKER_01] od svega toga što se događe.

788
00:31:51,440 --> 00:31:52,619
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, stvari je njemu najteže.

789
00:31:52,619 --> 00:31:53,660
[SPEAKER_02] Da, zato kažem.

790
00:31:53,720 --> 00:31:54,559
[SPEAKER_02] On je krajnja žrtva.

791
00:31:54,559 --> 00:31:57,539
[SPEAKER_02] Nikako, nikako.

792
00:31:57,539 --> 00:31:58,640
[SPEAKER_02] Ne znam.

793
00:31:58,640 --> 00:32:00,720
[SPEAKER_02] Ja bih lagala da kad bi sad rekla

794
00:32:00,720 --> 00:32:02,000
[SPEAKER_02] ja sam super nosim s time.

795
00:32:02,000 --> 00:32:03,680
[SPEAKER_02] Ne, ja sam u raspadu,

796
00:32:03,680 --> 00:32:04,819
[SPEAKER_02] ali ovoga...

797
00:32:04,819 --> 00:32:05,720
[SPEAKER_02] Ne vidi za to na vano.

798
00:32:05,720 --> 00:32:07,799
[SPEAKER_01] Držim glavu iznad vode.

799
00:32:07,799 --> 00:32:09,799
[SPEAKER_02] Trudim se držati glavu iznad vode.

800
00:32:09,799 --> 00:32:13,099
[SPEAKER_02] Puno je posla.

801
00:32:13,099 --> 00:32:15,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sam pedantna.

802
00:32:15,559 --> 00:32:17,220
[SPEAKER_02] Od tih sam ljudi.

803
00:32:17,220 --> 00:32:18,200
[SPEAKER_02] Trudim se biti pedantna.

804
00:32:18,200 --> 00:32:19,240
[SPEAKER_02] Želim uvijek sve proučiti.

805
00:32:19,240 --> 00:32:20,299
[SPEAKER_02] Prije nego što kažem,

806
00:32:20,299 --> 00:32:21,799
[SPEAKER_02] ne stižem uvijek sve.

807
00:32:21,799 --> 00:32:23,319
[SPEAKER_02] I puno je toga.

808
00:32:23,400 --> 00:32:24,380
[SPEAKER_02] Ali stvarno se trudim.

809
00:32:24,380 --> 00:32:26,180
[SPEAKER_02] I to me dosta opterečujem.

810
00:32:26,180 --> 00:32:28,240
[SPEAKER_02] A beba je jako mala

811
00:32:28,240 --> 00:32:29,599
[SPEAKER_02] i beba ništa ne spava.

812
00:32:29,599 --> 00:32:31,220
[SPEAKER_02] Sad oni rojitelji

813
00:32:31,220 --> 00:32:32,299
[SPEAKER_02] koji su imali taj slučaj

814
00:32:32,299 --> 00:32:33,140
[SPEAKER_02] znaju šta je to.

815
00:32:33,140 --> 00:32:35,039
[SPEAKER_02] A neki su uspjele to izbjeć

816
00:32:35,039 --> 00:32:37,339
[SPEAKER_02] pa misle da je ne spavanje

817
00:32:37,339 --> 00:32:39,019
[SPEAKER_02] jedan put ili dva put buđenje po noći.

818
00:32:39,019 --> 00:32:39,279
[SPEAKER_02] Nije.

819
00:32:39,279 --> 00:32:41,259
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sam svake noći budna

820
00:32:41,259 --> 00:32:42,359
[SPEAKER_02] po nekoliko sati

821
00:32:42,359 --> 00:32:43,819
[SPEAKER_02] i budim se po desetak puta.

822
00:32:43,819 --> 00:32:46,279
[SPEAKER_02] Tako da, ne znam,

823
00:32:46,279 --> 00:32:47,720
[SPEAKER_02] postajem sve gora osoba.

824
00:32:47,720 --> 00:32:49,819
[SPEAKER_02] Nemoj, molim ti,

825
00:32:49,819 --> 00:32:51,079
[SPEAKER_02] da to zaostavimo ovdje.

826
00:32:51,079 --> 00:32:53,339
[SPEAKER_00] Da ću neko dublje ispovje.

827
00:32:53,339 --> 00:32:56,440
[SPEAKER_00] Ne bi to već zanimljivo.

828
00:32:56,440 --> 00:32:58,140
[SPEAKER_00] Ja mislim da je ovo veliki izazov,

829
00:32:58,140 --> 00:32:59,920
[SPEAKER_00] ali da je to i jako zanimljivo

830
00:32:59,920 --> 00:33:00,859
[SPEAKER_00] vrijeme tvojeg života.

831
00:33:00,859 --> 00:33:02,980
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim sad imaš jednu prekrasnu bebu,

832
00:33:02,980 --> 00:33:04,140
[SPEAKER_00] danicu, jel?

833
00:33:04,140 --> 00:33:05,799
[SPEAKER_00] Jer te i ona motivirala da...

834
00:33:05,799 --> 00:33:08,440
[SPEAKER_02] Naravno, ona koliko god djete crpi,

835
00:33:08,440 --> 00:33:09,779
[SPEAKER_02] više od svega djete da je stavljivo.

836
00:33:09,779 --> 00:33:10,759
[SPEAKER_02] Na dahnju, da.

837
00:33:10,759 --> 00:33:15,440
[SPEAKER_02] Jer jednostavno, koliko god da vas neko i živci,

838
00:33:15,440 --> 00:33:17,039
[SPEAKER_02] ali mislite da je nešto važno,

839
00:33:17,039 --> 00:33:19,160
[SPEAKER_02] kada vidite to djete,

840
00:33:19,160 --> 00:33:20,140
[SPEAKER_02] samo je ono važno.

841
00:33:20,140 --> 00:33:21,180
[SPEAKER_02] I to znate,

842
00:33:21,180 --> 00:33:22,599
[SPEAKER_02] to je jedina istina.

843
00:33:22,599 --> 00:33:24,839
[SPEAKER_02] I onda je s time puno lakše

844
00:33:24,839 --> 00:33:26,279
[SPEAKER_02] podnositi sve ostalo

845
00:33:26,279 --> 00:33:27,380
[SPEAKER_02] i daj vam smisao

846
00:33:27,380 --> 00:33:28,960
[SPEAKER_02] da se borite za nešto.

847
00:33:28,960 --> 00:33:31,480
[SPEAKER_02] Tako da je to puno više blagoslov

848
00:33:31,480 --> 00:33:32,460
[SPEAKER_02] nego žrtva

849
00:33:32,460 --> 00:33:34,380
[SPEAKER_02] unatoč ovo moje prethodnoj kuknjavi

850
00:33:34,380 --> 00:33:35,640
[SPEAKER_02] koja je sramotna.

851
00:33:35,640 --> 00:33:37,220
[SPEAKER_02] Imajući u vidu da imam jedno djete,

852
00:33:37,220 --> 00:33:38,180
[SPEAKER_02] a žene se bore

853
00:33:38,180 --> 00:33:40,460
[SPEAKER_02] i u puno težim uvjetima

854
00:33:40,460 --> 00:33:42,500
[SPEAKER_02] i sa puno težim poslovima

855
00:33:42,500 --> 00:33:43,059
[SPEAKER_02] i sa puno više djeca.

856
00:33:43,059 --> 00:33:43,579
[SPEAKER_02] Dobro, to nema veze.

857
00:33:43,579 --> 00:33:45,859
[SPEAKER_00] Svako od nas za sebe ima jedno djete isto.

858
00:33:45,859 --> 00:33:48,339
[SPEAKER_00] Svako djete je teško imati jedno djete i dvoje.

859
00:33:48,339 --> 00:33:49,220
[SPEAKER_00] Djeca su različite,

860
00:33:49,220 --> 00:33:51,700
[SPEAKER_02] ali moram pokušati biti poštena.

861
00:33:51,700 --> 00:33:54,220
[SPEAKER_00] Ali uz Ninu,

862
00:33:54,359 --> 00:33:57,880
[SPEAKER_00] spomenula si da ti mama tvoja puno pomaže.

863
00:33:57,880 --> 00:33:59,500
[SPEAKER_02] Je, da nema mame.

864
00:33:59,500 --> 00:34:00,839
[SPEAKER_02] Blagoslovljene mame.

865
00:34:00,839 --> 00:34:03,539
[SPEAKER_02] Da, da, čita život bježiš od roditelja,

866
00:34:03,539 --> 00:34:05,019
[SPEAKER_02] pokušavaš se emancipirati,

867
00:34:05,019 --> 00:34:07,900
[SPEAKER_02] a onda na kraju shvatiš da su roditelji spas.

868
00:34:07,900 --> 00:34:09,079
[SPEAKER_02] Je, puno mi pomaže mama.

869
00:34:09,079 --> 00:34:11,940
[SPEAKER_02] Zaista, da mi mama ne uskače,

870
00:34:11,940 --> 00:34:12,739
[SPEAKER_02] ne bih mogla.

871
00:34:12,739 --> 00:34:14,260
[SPEAKER_02] Ne bih mogla nikako.

872
00:34:14,260 --> 00:34:15,280
[SPEAKER_02] I naravno i Nino je tu.

873
00:34:15,280 --> 00:34:17,239
[SPEAKER_02] Nino je što se tiče roditeljstva

874
00:34:17,239 --> 00:34:18,539
[SPEAKER_02] vrlo predan

875
00:34:18,539 --> 00:34:21,099
[SPEAKER_02] i jako, jako to voli.

876
00:34:21,099 --> 00:34:23,519
[SPEAKER_02] Tako da se mogu tu potpuno

877
00:34:23,519 --> 00:34:24,420
[SPEAKER_02] na njega osloniti.

878
00:34:24,420 --> 00:34:26,300
[SPEAKER_02] Samo to je jedno izazovno vrijeme.

879
00:34:26,300 --> 00:34:27,579
[SPEAKER_02] Ali u život uvijek sve dolazi

880
00:34:27,579 --> 00:34:29,460
[SPEAKER_02] ili u velikim količinama

881
00:34:29,460 --> 00:34:30,519
[SPEAKER_02] ili nikako.

882
00:34:30,519 --> 00:34:32,320
[SPEAKER_02] I nekako, nema veze.

883
00:34:32,320 --> 00:34:32,699
[SPEAKER_02] Pa da.

884
00:34:32,699 --> 00:34:35,199
[SPEAKER_00] A kako ove podjele, dakle,

885
00:34:35,199 --> 00:34:37,360
[SPEAKER_00] na konzervativne, liberalne, desno, ljevo,

886
00:34:37,360 --> 00:34:38,659
[SPEAKER_00] gdje ti sebe tu vidiš?

887
00:34:38,659 --> 00:34:40,360
[SPEAKER_00] Više puta si to tumačila,

888
00:34:40,360 --> 00:34:41,260
[SPEAKER_00] uvijek sam imala da vam

889
00:34:41,260 --> 00:34:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] nekako ne kažeš to,

890
00:34:43,000 --> 00:34:44,980
[SPEAKER_00] nekako da ne dorekneš do kraja.

891
00:34:44,980 --> 00:34:47,099
[SPEAKER_00] Pa mi sad, ne da nisi htjela,

892
00:34:47,099 --> 00:34:49,360
[SPEAKER_00] već da jednostavno emisije su bile takvog formata.

893
00:34:49,679 --> 00:34:51,420
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje ti sebe tu vidiš u stvari?

894
00:34:51,420 --> 00:34:53,099
[SPEAKER_00] Kako Marija to vidi sebe?

895
00:34:53,099 --> 00:34:55,260
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle, sad, kad bi se krenula

896
00:34:55,260 --> 00:34:56,800
[SPEAKER_02] pravit pametna, pa išta govorit

897
00:34:56,800 --> 00:34:58,360
[SPEAKER_02] da ti pojmovi ne znače ono

898
00:34:58,360 --> 00:34:59,500
[SPEAKER_02] što zvuče,

899
00:34:59,500 --> 00:35:01,019
[SPEAKER_02] onda bi opet komplicirala.

900
00:35:01,019 --> 00:35:03,559
[SPEAKER_02] A živim u stvarnosti

901
00:35:03,559 --> 00:35:05,179
[SPEAKER_02] i svjesna sam da šta god rekla,

902
00:35:05,179 --> 00:35:06,219
[SPEAKER_02] ljudi opet ljude dijele

903
00:35:06,219 --> 00:35:07,500
[SPEAKER_02] na ljevo i na desno.

904
00:35:07,500 --> 00:35:09,820
[SPEAKER_02] I sad mogla reći

905
00:35:09,820 --> 00:35:10,719
[SPEAKER_02] ljevo ne znači ljevo,

906
00:35:10,719 --> 00:35:11,300
[SPEAKER_02] nego to i to,

907
00:35:11,300 --> 00:35:12,300
[SPEAKER_02] desno ne znači desno,

908
00:35:12,300 --> 00:35:12,679
[SPEAKER_02] nego to i to.

909
00:35:12,679 --> 00:35:13,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ali to je orijentacija.

910
00:35:13,559 --> 00:35:15,019
[SPEAKER_02] Da, ljudima to je orijentacija.

911
00:35:15,019 --> 00:35:17,619
[SPEAKER_02] Ja nemam nikav problem

912
00:35:17,619 --> 00:35:18,699
[SPEAKER_02] s time da budem

913
00:35:18,699 --> 00:35:19,920
[SPEAKER_02] ili ljevo ili desno.

914
00:35:19,920 --> 00:35:21,719
[SPEAKER_02] Da pa će,

915
00:35:21,719 --> 00:35:23,619
[SPEAKER_02] što smatram da ispremo,

916
00:35:23,619 --> 00:35:24,280
[SPEAKER_02] to zagovaram.

917
00:35:24,280 --> 00:35:25,500
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sam negdje centar

918
00:35:25,500 --> 00:35:26,960
[SPEAKER_02] i sad ne mislim da to je

919
00:35:26,960 --> 00:35:28,239
[SPEAKER_02] ispražnjena funkcija

920
00:35:28,239 --> 00:35:29,360
[SPEAKER_02] i ono ljudi isto,

921
00:35:29,360 --> 00:35:30,880
[SPEAKER_02] mislim ja isto da to nisam,

922
00:35:30,880 --> 00:35:31,860
[SPEAKER_02] ja sad kad bi neko rekao

923
00:35:31,860 --> 00:35:32,280
[SPEAKER_02] da je centar,

924
00:35:32,280 --> 00:35:34,079
[SPEAKER_02] ja bih da reći šta si.

925
00:35:34,500 --> 00:35:35,579
[SPEAKER_02] Nemo, svi su centar,

926
00:35:35,579 --> 00:35:36,460
[SPEAKER_02] desni centar,

927
00:35:36,460 --> 00:35:37,559
[SPEAKER_02] ono, svi su centar,

928
00:35:37,559 --> 00:35:38,420
[SPEAKER_02] ljevi centar,

929
00:35:38,420 --> 00:35:39,199
[SPEAKER_02] desni centar,

930
00:35:39,199 --> 00:35:40,440
[SPEAKER_02] svi love u mutnom

931
00:35:40,440 --> 00:35:41,360
[SPEAKER_02] jer misle da se tamo

932
00:35:41,360 --> 00:35:41,780
[SPEAKER_02] svi negdje nalaze.

933
00:35:41,780 --> 00:35:42,239
[SPEAKER_02] A Andrej Plenković je

934
00:35:42,239 --> 00:35:42,719
[SPEAKER_02] desni centar.

935
00:35:42,719 --> 00:35:44,500
[SPEAKER_02] Da, on je i desni

936
00:35:44,500 --> 00:35:45,340
[SPEAKER_02] i ljevi centar.

937
00:35:45,340 --> 00:35:45,860
[SPEAKER_02] I ljevi centar, da.

938
00:35:45,860 --> 00:35:46,940
[SPEAKER_02] I centar desnog

939
00:35:46,940 --> 00:35:47,780
[SPEAKER_02] i ljevog centara.

940
00:35:47,780 --> 00:35:49,159
[SPEAKER_02] I centar svega.

941
00:35:49,159 --> 00:35:50,380
[SPEAKER_02] Sigurno središte toga,

942
00:35:50,380 --> 00:35:51,199
[SPEAKER_02] da, točno tako.

943
00:35:51,199 --> 00:35:51,820
[SPEAKER_02] Sigurno središte toga svega.

944
00:35:51,820 --> 00:35:53,019
[SPEAKER_02] Pomisle smo na isto, da.

